{"lemma":"خَرِبَةٍ","slug":"خَرِبَةٍ","root":"خ.ر.ب","root_slug":"خ-ر-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ر-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10242","n10243","n10244","n10245","n10246"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to demolish, devastate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to pierce, bore (especially the ears)"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"ruined, wrecked, destroyed","examples":[{"text":"The sun was sinking down over the sea, the mountain wall with all its clefts and promontories wore a cloak of many colours, when we saw before us on a rock a ruined tower.","english":"The Tragedy"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic. Compare Aramaic חֲרוֹב (“be laid waste”), Classical Syriac ܚܪܒ (“be laid waste”), Hebrew חָרַב (kharáv, “to be destroyed”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10242","headword_ar":"خَرْبَةٌ","root":"xrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"see the next paragraph, in two places.       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xirobapN","text_ar":"خِرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n10243","headword_ar":"خُرْبَةٌ","root":"xrb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A hole, perforation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bore;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whether round or not:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any round hole"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perforation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bore;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as that of the ear;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) [and] so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobN","text_ar":"خُرْبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A:) pl. [of mult.] of the former (in this and in other senses here following, K, * TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurabN","text_ar":"خُرَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuruwbN","text_ar":"خُرُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which latter is extr. [with respect to rule], and [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoraAbN","text_ar":"اَخْرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is irregular as pl. of the former, but regular as pl. of the latter]. (K. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurotN","text_ar":"خُرْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurotapN","text_ar":"خُرْتَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobapN","text_ar":"خُرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~inodiY~i","text_ar":"السِّنْدِىِّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The bore of the lobe of the ear, when not slit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the Sindee being particularly noted by the Arabs for his pierced ears:]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when slit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"it is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~inodiY~i","text_ar":"السِّنْدِىِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarobapN","text_ar":"خَرْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Width of the hole,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perforation, of the ear;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarobN","text_ar":"خَرْبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobN","text_ar":"خُرْبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axorabN","text_ar":"اَخْرَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) this last being a subst. like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afokalN","text_ar":"اَفْكَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eye"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a needle: [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurotN","text_ar":"خُرْتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurotapN","text_ar":"خُرْتَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foramen"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the anus: as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobN","text_ar":"خُرْبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarobN","text_ar":"خَرْبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xar~aAbapN","text_ar":"خَرَّابَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xur~aAbapN","text_ar":"خُرَّابَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuraAbapN","text_ar":"خُرَابَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, MF;) in both of these senses, though this is not clearly shown in the K: (MF:) and likewise, of the vagina; the dual of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobapN","text_ar":"خُرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurring in a trad., as some relate it, applied to the foramen of the anus and that of the vagina together: (TA:) and the last, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuraAbapN","text_ar":"خُرَابَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any perforation like the eye of a needle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxurobapu","text_ar":"الخُرْبَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxurobu","text_ar":"الخُرْبُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxuraAbapu","text_ar":"الخُرَابَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxur~aAbapu","text_ar":"الخُرَّابَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The hole"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"socket"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the hip,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"where the head of the thigh-bone is inserted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobapu Alwariki","text_ar":"خُرْبَةُ الوَرِكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwrk","text_ar":"الورك"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobu","text_ar":"خُرْبُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarobu","text_ar":"خَرْبُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwrk","text_ar":"الورك"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwrk","text_ar":"الورك"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraAbapu","text_ar":"خَرَابَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or, probably, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuraAbap","text_ar":"خُرَابَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwrk","text_ar":"الورك"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xur~aAbapu","text_ar":"خُرَّابَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwrk","text_ar":"الورك"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xar~aAbapu","text_ar":"خَرَّابَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": and the pl.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axoraAbN","text_ar":"اَخْرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", also signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower extremities of the shoulder-blades."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxurobapu","text_ar":"الخُرْبَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A 'Obeyd, S, Mgh, Msb, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobapu AlmazaAdap","text_ar":"خُرْبَةُ المَزَادَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxur~aAbap","text_ar":"الخُرَّابَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and sometimes ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxuraAbap","text_ar":"الخُرَابَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"without tesh-deed, (TA,) [and perhaps ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxurobu","text_ar":"الخُرْبُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xubonN","text_ar":"خُبْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The loop of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leathern water-bag called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mazaAdap","text_ar":"مَزَادَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A 'Obeyd, S, A, Mgh, Msb, K;) because of its round form: every"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mzAdp","text_ar":"مزادة"},{"kind":"text","text":"having two loops [whereby it is suspended upon either side of the camel], each of which is thus called; and two kidney-shaped pieces of leather ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuloyataAni","text_ar":"كُلْيَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":") [at the two upper corners]; and the two loops are sewed to these. (TA. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurotapN","text_ar":"خُرْتَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A vice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fault;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAth, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarabapN","text_ar":"خَرَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corruption,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsoundness, in religion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarabapN","text_ar":"خَرَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarobapN","text_ar":"خَرْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarobapN","text_ar":"حَرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Mgh, * K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobN","text_ar":"خُرْبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarobN","text_ar":"خَرْبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarabN","text_ar":"خَرَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a quality inducing suspicion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil opinion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a meaning app. belonging to all of the foregoing words:] (TA:) pl., of the first,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurubaAtN","text_ar":"خُرُبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and of the second,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarabaAtN","text_ar":"خَرَبَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (JK:) also, the first (i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobapN","text_ar":"خُرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a crime: a bad, an evil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a foul, word"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saying:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a trial,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an affliction."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA fiyhi xurobapN","text_ar":"مَا فِيهِ خُرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not in him a vice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fault."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA raA^ayonaA mino fulaAnK","text_ar":"مَا رَاَيْنَا مِنْ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobapF","text_ar":"خُرْبَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarobFA","text_ar":"خَرْبًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarabapF","text_ar":"خَرَبَةً","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We have not seen in such a one unsoundness of religion nor anything disgraceful."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAr~N bixurobapK","text_ar":"فَارٌّ بِخُرْبَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", occurring in a trad., means One"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who flees with a thing desiring to appropriate it to himself and to take possession of it unlawfully."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","A","Msb","K","JK","MF","S"]},{"entry_id":"n10244","headword_ar":"خِرْبَةٌ","root":"xrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraAbN","text_ar":"خَرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places.       -A2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"guise, of him who is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAribN","text_ar":"خَارِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) also explained as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing whereof one is ashamed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or as derived from ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarabapN","text_ar":"خَرَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning] “ contemptibleness, and disgrace, or ignominy: ” or it may be ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarobapN","text_ar":"خَرْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a single act"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a shamefal nature,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Et-Tirmidhee, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K"]},{"entry_id":"n10245","headword_ar":"خَرَبَةٌ","root":"xrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobapN","text_ar":"خُرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places, near the end of the paragraph. ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*il~apN","text_ar":"ذِلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Baseness, vileness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: (K, TA:) in one copy of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zal~apN","text_ar":"زَلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a slip, lapse, fault,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: (TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disgrace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ignominy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contemptibleness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlxarabapN","text_ar":"الخَرَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEaworapu","text_ar":"العَوْرَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"parts, of the person, which it is indecent to expose"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n10246","headword_ar":"خَرِبَةٌ","root":"xrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and its pls.: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraAbN","text_ar":"خَرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in five places."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}